{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:1",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ",
      "translation": "1. Seseorang bertanya tentang azab yang pasti terjadi,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:2",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ",
      "translation": "2. bagi orang-orang kafir, yang tidak seorang pun dapat menolaknya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:3",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ",
      "translation": "3. (Azab) dari Allah, yang memiliki tempat-tempat naik.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:4",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ",
      "translation": "4. Para malaikat dan Jibril naik (menghadap) kepada Tuhan, dalam sehari setara dengan lima puluh ribu tahun.*(863)",
      "footnotes": "*863). Para malaikat dan Jibril menghadap Tuhan memakan waktu satu hari. Apabila dilakukan oleh manusia, memakan waktu lima puluh ribu tahun."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:5",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا",
      "translation": "5. Maka bersabarlah engkau (Muhammad) dengan kesabaran yang baik.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:6",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا",
      "translation": "6. Mereka memandang (azab) itu jauh (mustahil).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:7",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا",
      "translation": "7. Sedangkan Kami memandangnya dekat (pasti terjadi).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:8",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ تَكُونُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ كَٱلۡمُهۡلِ",
      "translation": "8. (Ingatlah) pada hari ketika langit menjadi bagaikan cairan tembaga,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:9",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ",
      "translation": "9. Dan gunung-gunung bagaikan bulu (yang beterbangan),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:10",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَا يَسۡـَٔلُ حَمِيمٌ حَمِيمٗا",
      "translation": "10. Dan tidak ada seorang teman karib pun menanyakan temannya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:11",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يُبَصَّرُونَهُمۡۚ يَوَدُّ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُ لَوۡ يَفۡتَدِي مِنۡ عَذَابِ يَوۡمِئِذِۭ بِبَنِيهِ",
      "translation": "11. Sedang mereka saling melihat. Pada hari itu, orang yang berdosa ingin sekiranya ia dapat menebus (dirinya) dari azab dengan anak-anaknya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:12",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ",
      "translation": "12. Dan istrinya dan saudaranya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:13",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ",
      "translation": "13. Dan keluarga yang melindunginya (di dunia),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:14",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ",
      "translation": "14. Dan orang-orang di bumi seluruhnya, kemudian mengharapkan (tebusan) itu menyelamatkannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:15",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهَا لَظَىٰ",
      "translation": "15. Sama sekali tidak! Sungguh, neraka itu api yang bergejolak,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:16",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "نَزَّاعَةٗ لِّلشَّوَىٰ",
      "translation": "16. Yang mengelupaskan kulit kepala.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:17",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَدۡعُواْ مَنۡ أَدۡبَرَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "17. Yang memanggil orang yang membelakangi dan yang berpaling (dari agama),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:18",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَمَعَ فَأَوۡعَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "18. Dan orang yang mengumpulkan (harta benda) lalu menyimpannya.*(864)",
      "footnotes": "*864). Orang yang menyimpan hartanya dan tidak mau mengeluarkan zakat dan tidak pula menginfakkannya ke jalan yang benar."
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:19",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "۞ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعًا",
      "translation": "19. Sungguh, manusia diciptakan bersifat suka mengeluh.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:20",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ جَزُوعٗا",
      "translation": "20. Apabila dia ditimpa kesusahan dia berkeluh kesah,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:21",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلۡخَيۡرُ مَنُوعًا",
      "translation": "21. Dan apabila mendapat kebaikan (harta) dia jadi kikir,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:22",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ",
      "translation": "22. Kecuali orang-orang yang melaksanakan salat,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:23",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ دَآئِمُونَ",
      "translation": "23. Mereka yang tetap setia melaksanakan salatnya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:24",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ فِيٓ أَمۡوَٰلِهِمۡ حَقّٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ",
      "translation": "24. Dan orang-orang yang dalam hartanya disiapkan bagian tertentu,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:25",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّلسَّآئِلِ وَٱلۡمَحۡرُومِ",
      "translation": "25. Bagi orang (miskin) yang meminta dan tidak meminta,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:26",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ يُصَدِّقُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ",
      "translation": "26. Dan orang-orang yang mempercayai hari pembalasan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:27",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم مِّنۡ عَذَابِ رَبِّهِم مُّشۡفِقُونَ",
      "translation": "27. Dan orang-orang yang takut terhadap azab Tuhannya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:28",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّهِمۡ غَيۡرُ مَأۡمُونٖ",
      "translation": "28. Sesungguhnya terhadap azab Tuhan mereka, tidak ada seseorang yang merasa aman (dari kedatangannya),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:29",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِفُرُوجِهِمۡ حَٰفِظُونَ",
      "translation": "29. Dan orang-orang yang memelihara kemaluannya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:30",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ",
      "translation": "30. Kecuali terhadap istri-istri mereka atau hamba sahaya yang mereka miliki,*(865) maka sesungguhnya mereka tidak tercela.",
      "footnotes": "*865). Hamba sahaya yang didapat dalam peperangan dengan orang kafir. Dalam peperangan dengan orang-orang kafir itu, perempuan-perempuan yang ditawan biasanya dibagi-bagikan kepada kaum muslimin yang ikut dalam peperangan, dan kebiasaan ini bukanlah sesuatu yang diwajibkan."
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:31",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ",
      "translation": "31. Maka barangsiapa mencari di luar itu (seperti zina, homoseks, dan lesbian), mereka itulah yang melampaui batas.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:32",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ",
      "translation": "32. Dan orang-orang yang memelihara amanat dan janjinya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:33",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ",
      "translation": "33. dan orang-orang yang berpegang teguh pada kesaksiannya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:34",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ",
      "translation": "34. dan orang-orang yang memelihara salatnya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:35",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ",
      "translation": "35. Mereka itu dimuliakan di dalam surga.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:36",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ",
      "translation": "36. Maka mengapa orang-orang kafir itu datang bergegas ke hadapanmu (Muhammad),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:37",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ",
      "translation": "37. Dari kanan dan dari kiri dengan berkelompok-kelompok?*(866)",
      "footnotes": "*866). Menurut keterangan sebagian mufassir, ayat ini berhubungan dengan peristiwa ketika Rasulullah salat dan membaca Al-Qur`ān di dekat Ka`bah, lalu orang-orang musyrik berkumpul berkelompok-kelompok di hadapannya sambil mengejek dan mengatakan, “Jika orang-orang mukmin benar-benar akan masuk surga sebagaimana kata Muhammad, kitalah yang akan masuk terlebih dahulu.” Maka turunlah ayat 38."
    },
